**Note:** Replace `vpc-12345678`, `subnet-12345678`, `subnet-87654321`, and `example.com` with your actual VPC, subnet IDs, and domain name. To shift traffic, update the `weight` values (e.g., blue=0, green=100) and apply terraform.

