**Note:** This creates the Lex bot structure optimized for kids (child-directed, friendly voice, simple intents). You'll need to create the actual Lex intents, utterances, and sample responses through the AWS Console or CDK/CloudFormation for full functionality, as Terraform Lex support for detailed intent configuration is limited. The bot is ready for testing and integration! 🍕👶

