```

This configuration creates:
- A Route 53 hosted zone named "primary"
- Two endpoint records for US and EU regions
- A geolocation routing policy that routes `app.primary.example.com` to the nearest endpoint based on continent (US/NA → US endpoint, EU → EU endpoint)
- Default fallback to US endpoint

