This configuration creates a custom DAX parameter group named `my-custom-dax-param-group` with common customized parameters for query TTL (300 seconds), record TTL (60 seconds), and disables cluster discovery endpoint. You can modify the parameters list based on your specific requirements. Reference this parameter group when creating DAX clusters using `parameter_group_name = aws_dax_parameter_group.custom.name`.

