**Note:** Create a `userdata.sh` file in the same directory with basic web server setup:

```bash
#!/bin/bash
yum update -y
yum install -y httpd
systemctl start httpd
systemctl enable httpd
echo "<h1>Video Streaming Server - $(hostname)</h1>" > /var/www/html/index.html
```

