```

**Prerequisites:**
1. Create an SSH key pair on your local machine: `ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 2048 -f ~/.ssh/lightsail_key`
2. Update the `public_key` path in the code to point to your `lightsail_key.pub` file
3. Adjust `region`, `availability_zone`, `blueprint_id`, and `bundle_id` as needed
4. Run `terraform init`, `terraform plan`, `terraform apply`

