This configuration creates an AWS Aurora PostgreSQL cluster with **storage autoscaling enabled**:

- **`storage_auto_scaling_enabled = true`** - Automatically scales storage when needed
- **`max_allocated_storage = 1000`** - Maximum 1TB storage limit
- **Initial storage**: 100GB
- Multi-AZ deployment for high availability
- Proper VPC, subnets, and security group setup

The cluster will automatically scale storage up to 1TB when utilization approaches 90% without downtime.

