```

**Note:** Replace `aws_vpc.main.id` with your existing VPC ID if you already have one. The Egress-Only Internet Gateway (`aws_egress_only_internet_gateway`) is the key resource that enables outbound IPv6-only internet access without allowing inbound traffic. The IPv6 route `::/0` must be added to a route table associated with your subnets.

